    <title>部署靜態個人網頁</title>
    <url>/posts/5465/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="/image/gallery/5465/01.png"
                     
                ></p>
<h2 id="克隆倉庫"><a href="#克隆倉庫" class="headerlink" title="克隆倉庫"></a>克隆倉庫</h2><ol>
<li>訪問<a class="link"   href="https://github.com/JerryIs-strong/personal-webpage" >JerryIs-strong&#x2F;personal-webpage <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></li>
<li>點擊<code>Fork</code></li>
<li>點擊<code>Create fork</code></li>
<li>此項目成功克隆至你的倉庫</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><ol>
<li>根據<a class="link"   href="https://github.com/JerryIs-strong/personal-webpage?tab=readme-ov-file#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%A0%85" >文檔 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a>對<code>setting.json</code>經行修改</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h2><ol>
<li>以<a class="link"   href="https://medium.com/flycode/how-to-deploy-a-static-website-for-free-using-github-pages-8eddc194853b" >Github Page部署 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></li>
<li>以<a class="link"   href="https://alphasec.io/how-to-deploy-a-static-website-with-netlify/" >Netlify部署 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></li>
<li>以<a class="link"   href="https://stefankudla.com/posts/how-to-deploy-a-static-html-css-and-javascript-website-to-vercel" >Vercel部署 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
